1. import libraries numbpy, pandas , matplotlib, sklearn
  2. Read dataset
  3. Understand data info, describe, dtypes, isNull, isNullSum, shape
  4. Visulization a. Histogram on x-axis cgpa, y-axis students b. Bar charts cgpa on x-axis, y-axis students c. Piechart research experience (Yes, no) or on piechart on cgpa optional
  5. Splitting your data into train and test
  6. Apply decision tree and evaluate its performance

Data set link: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/mohansacharya/graduate-admissions?resource=download
